Package: mkpdf
Version: 1.0-1
Section: base
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: texlive-latex-base, texlive-lang-arabic, texlive-fonts-recommended,
 texlive-xetex, lmodern, xzdec, evince, gedit, gedit-plugins, gedit-latex-plugin
Maintainer: github.com/ID
Description: produces PDF documents using the LaTeX/XeTeX compilers.
 *builds a PDF from a LAtin <.tex> document.
 *builds a PDF from a FArsi <.tex> document.
 *sorts out the list of references using the BibTeX tool.
 *installs a CTAN package.
 *installs font(s).
 *provides a collection of sample <.tex> documents.
